* {{cite web|first=Jeff|last=Bridges |url=http://time.com/2809276/notallmen-dont-get-it/ |title=#NotAllMen Don't Get It |website=[[Time (magazine)|TIME]] |publisher=[[Meredith Corporation]]|location=New York City|date=June 2, 2014 |accessdate=July 13, 2014}}
* {{cite web|first=Phil|last=Plait |url=http://www.slate.com/blogs/bad_astronomy/2014/05/27/not_all_men_how_discussing_women_s_issues_gets_derailed.html |title=Not all men: How discussing women’s issues gets derailed |website=[[Slate.com]] |publisher=[[The Slate Group]]|location=New York City|date=May 27, 2014 |accessdate=July 13, 2014}}
* {{cite web|first=Monica|last=Vendituoli |url=http://chronicle.com/article/NotAllMen-but-YesAllWomen-/146811/ |title=#NotAllMen, but #YesAllWomen: Campus Tragedy Spurs Debate on Sexual Violence |website=[[Chronicle of Higher Education]]|publisher=The Chronicle of Higher Education Inc.|location=Washington DC|date=May 28, 2014 |accessdate=July 13, 2014}}
